snippet.title: Scathe - Game Official Gameplay Teaser (Sept 2020) - Coming Soon
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM NOW!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1154830/Scathe/
Scathe is an FPS on steriods. A Hell initiation test like no other for up to four co-op players. Grab insane weapons, find the four Hellstones, mow down everything in your way and escape. If you're good enough...
